OL,6,F"We're not watering anything down,
OL,7,Fwe're actually increasing and
OL,8,Fstrengthening the action that we are
OL,9,Ftaking," she said.
OL,11,F"So we're setting out we're supporting
OL,12,Flocal inquiries, we've announced that
OL,13,Fthe first one will be Oldham, but
OL,14,Fthere will be other local inquiries,
OL,15,Fwe're setting out the framework.
