OL,3,CGrooming gangs probe to 'go ahead'
OL,4,Cdespite 'watering down' claims
OL,6,F"We've always said we would also do
OL,7,Fmore to support victims and survivors
OL,8,Fand we're actually announcing
OL,9,Fadditional therapeutic support will be
OL,10,Fprovided for victims and survivors of
OL,11,Fawful child abuse and exploitation."
OL,13,FThe framework which will support the
OL,14,Finquiry in Oldham, and can be applied
OL,15,Fto other reviews, will be published
OL,16,Fnext month, the Home Office said.
