OL,3,CGrooming gangs probe to 'go ahead'
OL,4,Cdespite 'watering down' claims
OL,6,FQuestions about whether the inquiries
OL,7,Fwould not go ahead arose when
OL,8,Fsafeguarding minister Jess Phillips
OL,9,Fdid not provide an update on them in
OL,10,Fthe Commons, as she briefed MPs on the
OL,11,FGovernment's latest steps to tackle
OL,12,Fchild grooming on Tuesday 8 April.
OL,14,FMs Phillips told MPs that local
OL,15,Fauthorities will be able to access a
OL,16,F#5 million fund to support locally-led
OL,17,Fwork on grooming gangs.
