OL,3,CGrooming gangs probe to 'go ahead'
OL,4,Cdespite 'watering down' claims
OL,6,FShe added that "following feedback"
OL,7,Ffrom local authorities, the fund will
OL,8,Fhave a flexible approach to support
OL,9,Findependent local inquiries as well as
OL,10,Fvictims' panels or locally-led audits
OL,11,Finto the handling of historic cases.
OL,13,FAfter the statement, Conservative
OL,14,Ffrontbencher Katie Lam said local
OL,15,Finquiries are not good enough and
OL,16,Fclaimed the Government is "watering
OL,17,Fthem down even further".
