OL,3,CGrooming gangs probe to 'go ahead'
OL,4,Cdespite 'watering down' claims
OL,6,FSir Trevor Phillips, the former
OL,7,Fchairman of the Equality and Human
OL,8,FRights Commission, also hit out at the
OL,9,FGovernment's approach as "utterly
OL,10,Fshameful".
OL,12,FSpeaking on Good Morning Britain Ms
OL,13,FCooper added that inquiries in
OL,14,Fthemselves were not enough and that
OL,15,Fpolice investigations into abuse would
OL,16,Falso be strengthened.
OL,18,FShe said:" These are the most terrible
OL,19,Fcrimes of all, we're talking about
OL,20,Frape, we're talking about coercion,
OL,21,Fwe're talking about exploitation.
