OL,3,CGrooming gangs probe to 'go ahead'
OL,4,Cdespite 'watering down' claims
OL,6,F"We have to have support for victims
OL,7,Fand survivors, we have to have local
OL,8,Finquiries where they are needed, but
OL,9,Fwe also crucially have to have police
OL,10,Finvestigations.
OL,12,F"The most important thing we are doing
OL,13,Fis increasing police investigations
OL,14,Finto these appalling, appalling crimes
OL,15,Fso that we get the perpetrators behind
OL,16,Fbars.
OL,18,F"That is the the justice that victims
OL,19,Fand survivors need to see, and that it
OL,20,Falso the way to keep communities safe."
