OL,3,CGrooming gangs probe to 'go ahead'
OL,4,Cdespite 'watering down' claims
OL,6,FThe move comes after the Independent
OL,7,FInquiry into Child Sexual Abuse
OL,8,F(IICSA), led by Professor Alexis Jay,
OL,9,Ffound institutional failings and tens
OL,10,Fof thousands of victims across England
OL,11,Fand Wales.
OL,13,FThe seven-year probe made 20
OL,14,Frecommendations in the final report
OL,15,Fpublished in 2022, as it described
OL,16,Fchild sexual abuse as an "epidemic"
OL,17,Facross the two nations.
