OL,3,CGrooming gangs probe to 'go ahead'
OL,4,Cdespite 'watering down' claims
OL,6,FThe Government had knocked back calls
OL,7,Ffor a national review in favour of
OL,8,Flocally-led inquiries, saying it was
OL,9,Ffocused on implementing
OL,10,Frecommendations from Prof Jay's report.
OL,12,FIt is understood an announcement on
OL,13,Fhow local authorities can apply for
OL,14,Ffunding will be made in due course.
