OL,3,CGrooming gangs probe to 'go ahead'
OL,4,Cdespite 'watering down' claims
OL,6,FA Home Office spokeswoman said: "The
OL,7,F#5m funding announced in January will
OL,8,Fsupport local authorities to
OL,9,Fstrengthen their responses to child
OL,10,Fsexual exploitation. All local
OL,11,Fauthorities will be able to apply for
OL,12,Ffunding for local inquiries.
OL,14,F"Any claims that the funding has been
OL,15,Fwatered down, or that we are backing
OL,16,Fdown from supporting local inquiries,
OL,17,Fis patently false. A flexible approach
OL,18,Fto funding will allow us to support
OL,19,Fmore than five inquiries."
